{"tid":1119251,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"炭爐雞蛋仔","createTime":"2019-04-21T19:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T07:28:20.000Z","uid":111088,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ac801ec8c048301e6ef4b9f89b6e9c16728922c0","tid":1119251,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqsSyaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqsSyaw.jpg&h=3f90222e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日街過九龍城見到街頭有一檔木頭車雞蛋仔<br />\n一對老夫妻經營嘅<br />\n喺架車度寫左大大隻字請勿攝影所以冇影到佢地<br />\n我俾佢地啲蛋雞仔同炭香撈埋嗰陣味吸引所以買左底<br />\n哇熱辣辣擺入口<br />\n脆卜卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外脆內軟<br />\n入面係漲卜卜唔係大大個窿嘅空心雞蛋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個味道有啲偏甜但係個texture係creamy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係炭爐先做得出嘅味道"},{"pid":"b07fae38857a156cecece532c73ba11e708a624b","tid":1119251,"uid":111088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:43:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n支持小店"},{"pid":"8f8cf7972e132cc590641f286bdb0336e527d979","tid":1119251,"uid":46863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T20:11:38.000Z","msg":"大約邊個位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b5415a48ebc26e429cdb4a19c914a5e4a91e04","tid":1119251,"uid":111088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8f8cf7972e132cc590641f286bdb0336e527d979","tid":1119251,"uid":46863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T20:11:38.000Z","msg":"大約邊個位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T20:16:49.000Z","msg":"九龍城廣場嗰邊間百佳附近"},{"pid":"91e5ace2b580b1dd2c587e5c7a914a01859dcdc7","tid":1119251,"uid":146435,"like":5,"dislike